  "body": "* Project GitHub tag: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/labels/LES\r\n\r\n### Project Vision\r\nAdd an option to use LES and ULC in our application. It should work on Ropsten and Mainnet with working discovery.\r\n\r\n### Project Scope\r\n* Have ULC and LES networks in the list of networks\r\n* LES and ULC should work stable\r\n* Minimum scope: Ropsten and Mainnet\r\n* User should be able to turn discovery on or off (can in in dev. settings)\r\n* User should be able to manage trusted peers for ULC from the UI\r\n* User should be able to create custom networks with LES compatibility\r\n* Low-hanging fruits performance optimizations should be included\r\n\r\n### Project Tradeoffs\r\n* Status can provide a cluster (or a fleet machines) with LES slots\r\n* ULC can use Status LES servers as trusted nodes\r\n\r\n### Stretch goals\r\n(maybe) ULC patch is merged upstream (go-ethereum)\r\n(maybe) LES fixes are merged upstream (go-ethereum)\r\n(maybe) Background App Refresh on iOS and Android is supported\r\n\r\n\r\n## Roadmap\r\n\r\nDeploy LES servers for Ropsten\r\n- [x] ~https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/5891~\r\n\r\nAdd LES/ULC as options (only using LES servers provided by Status) on Ropsten\r\n- [x] ~https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/6256~\r\n- [x] ~https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/6088~\r\n- [x] ~https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/6007~\r\n* [ULC] https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/6529\r\n\r\nMake sure that LES & ULC doesn't contain critical bugs on Ropsten\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-go/issues/1258\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-go/issues/1248\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6904\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6901\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6859\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6840\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6073\r\n\r\nDeploy and add monitoring to Mainnet LES servers (Status)\r\n\r\nAdd LES & ULC networks for Mainnet (only using LES server provided by Status)\r\n\r\nEnable discovery on Ropsten and Mainnet\r\n\r\n\r\nEnable user to create and manage LES/ULC networks\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6476\r\n\r\nAdd debugging UI\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6530\r\n* https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6479\r\n\r\nDocument and Knowledge-share ULC patch\r\n\r\nMake low-hanging fruit performance optimizations\r\n* TBD\r\n\r\n",
